WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.100 --> 00:00:01.900
Here you go.

2
00:00:09.333 --> 00:00:11.333
Mommy, I miss 4 treasures

3
00:00:11.333 --> 00:00:12.833
I can't eat anymore.

4
00:00:17.100 --> 00:00:18.466
5 children

5
00:00:20.400 --> 00:00:22.033
Lost one

6
00:00:22.800 --> 00:00:24.966
I sent another meal away

7
00:00:26.733 --> 00:00:27.700
This world

8
00:00:27.700 --> 00:00:30.200
How could there be such a useless mother as me?

9
00:00:32.400 --> 00:00:33.600
Four Treasures

10
00:00:34.500 --> 00:00:36.300
How are you doing now?

11
00:00:54.533 --> 00:00:55.666
Is it a pig?

12
00:00:55.666 --> 00:00:58.200
It doesn't matter who you are

13
00:00:58.200 --> 00:01:00.200
The important thing is that I owe you a favor

14
00:01:00.333 --> 00:01:02.000
So I investigated a few things for you.

15
00:01:02.000 --> 00:01:03.100
Your daughter is sick

16
00:01:03.100 --> 00:01:03.966
To treat him

17
00:01:03.966 --> 00:01:05.766
You gave him to a woman named Xia Lily

18
00:01:05.766 --> 00:01:07.166
How do you know that?

19
00:01:07.166 --> 00:01:08.500
You heard me

20
00:01:08.500 --> 00:01:11.400
You must bring your daughter back immediately

21
00:01:11.466 --> 00:01:13.566
You lost it five years ago

22
00:01:13.566 --> 00:01:15.266
If you lose it again this time

23
00:01:15.266 --> 00:01:16.966
You will regret it for the rest of your life

24
00:01:23.366 --> 00:01:25.900
Lily, this is really not what it used to be

25
00:01:25.900 --> 00:01:27.900
Compete with Xi Shao for the lamp

26
00:01:27.900 --> 00:01:30.000
We really got the light of lilies

27
00:01:30.100 --> 00:01:32.700
To actually have the opportunity to join hands with such a river god

28
00:01:32.700 --> 00:01:33.933
The richest man eats at the same table

29
00:01:33.933 --> 00:01:35.300
Can you speak?

30
00:01:35.400 --> 00:01:37.566
Lily is about to become Mrs. Xi

31
00:01:37.566 --> 00:01:39.066
Gotta change the title

32
00:01:39.333 --> 00:01:41.000
Yeah, yeah, yeah, look at my mouth

33
00:01:41.000 --> 00:01:42.766
I will punish myself with three cups to respect Mrs. Xi

34
00:01:42.766 --> 00:01:44.000
Then again

35
00:01:44.100 --> 00:01:44.900
Lily

36
00:01:45.000 --> 00:01:47.733
You and Xia Zhu were good sisters in college

37
00:01:47.733 --> 00:01:49.666
Are you getting married and not inviting him?

38
00:01:49.766 --> 00:01:51.866
You really don't open the milk jug

39
00:01:52.066 --> 00:01:54.166
Bet on half of college that year

40
00:01:54.166 --> 00:01:55.933
I went to have a baby with a wild man

41
00:01:55.933 --> 00:01:57.966
How can I have the face to come to the reunion?

42
00:01:58.666 --> 00:01:59.766
Okay, okay.

43
00:01:59.766 --> 00:02:01.566
Let's not talk about that.

44
00:02:01.700 --> 00:02:03.066
I'm going to make a call

45
00:02:03.800 --> 00:02:04.866
Handle some business

46
00:02:04.866 --> 00:02:05.666
Okay

47
00:02:06.766 --> 00:02:09.033
Today is my engagement party with Young Master Xi

48
00:02:09.100 --> 00:02:11.500
You can order whatever you want to eat

49
00:02:11.766 --> 00:02:13.600
Mrs. Xi is the atmosphere

50
00:02:16.166 --> 00:02:18.066
Xia Lily, what about my four treasures?

51
00:02:18.066 --> 00:02:19.266
I want to see the Four Treasures

